<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Analyst Safety Review -- SafeTrekr</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Every trip professionally reviewed across 17 safety sections by a trained analyst. Destination safety, transportation, emergency preparedness, and compliance -- nothing missed.">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Analyst Safety Review: 17 Sections, Nothing Missed">
  <meta property="og:description" content="SafeTrekr assigns a trained safety analyst to every trip. 17 structured review sections. 5 government data sources. Professional findings and recommendations delivered in your Safety Binder.">
  <meta property="og:image" content="/og/analyst-review.png">
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://safetrekr.com/platform/analyst-review">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="design-tokens.css">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script src="https://mcp.figma.com/mcp/html-to-design/capture.js" async></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            background: 'var(--color-background)',
            foreground: 'var(--color-foreground)',
            card: 'var(--color-card)',
            'card-foreground': 'var(--color-card-foreground)',
            border: 'var(--color-border)',
            input: 'var(--color-input)',
            ring: 'var(--color-ring)',
            muted: 'var(--color-muted)',
            'muted-foreground': 'var(--color-muted-foreground)',
            accent: 'var(--color-accent)',
            'accent-foreground': 'var(--color-accent-foreground)',
            primary: {
              50: 'var(--color-primary-50)',
              100: 'var(--color-primary-100)',
              200: 'var(--color-primary-200)',
              300: 'var(--color-primary-300)',
              400: 'var(--color-primary-400)',
              500: 'var(--color-primary-500)',
              600: 'var(--color-primary-600)',
              700: 'var(--color-primary-700)',
              800: 'var(--color-primary-800)',
              900: 'var(--color-primary-900)',
              950: 'var(--color-primary-950)',
              DEFAULT: 'var(--color-primary)',
            },
            secondary: {
              DEFAULT: 'var(--color-secondary)',
              foreground: 'var(--color-secondary-foreground)',
              light: 'var(--color-secondary-light)',
              muted: 'var(--color-secondary-muted)',
            },
            destructive: {
              DEFAULT: 'var(--color-destructive)',
              foreground: 'var(--color-destructive-foreground)',
            },
            safety: {
              green: 'var(--color-safety-green)',
              yellow: 'var(--color-safety-yellow)',
              red: 'var(--color-safety-red)',
            },
          },
          fontFamily: {
            display: ['Plus Jakarta Sans', 'system-ui', '-apple-system', 'sans-serif'],
            body: ['Inter', 'system-ui', '-apple-system', 'sans-serif'],
            mono: ['JetBrains Mono', 'ui-monospace', 'monospace'],
          },
          borderRadius: {
            sm: 'var(--radius-sm)',
            md: 'var(--radius-md)',
            lg: 'var(--radius-lg)',
            xl: 'var(--radius-xl)',
            '2xl': 'var(--radius-2xl)',
          },
          boxShadow: {
            xs: 'var(--shadow-xs)',
            sm: 'var(--shadow-sm)',
            md: 'var(--shadow-md)',
            lg: 'var(--shadow-lg)',
            xl: 'var(--shadow-xl)',
          },
          maxWidth: {
            'container': '1280px',
          },
        },
      },
    }
  </script>

  <!-- JSON-LD: FAQPage + Service -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@graph": [
      {
        "@type": "FAQPage",
        "mainEntity": [
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Who are the safety analysts?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Every SafeTrekr analyst is a trained professional who has completed our structured training program covering risk assessment methodology, government intelligence interpretation, and the 17-section review framework."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How long does a review take?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Most reviews are completed in 3-5 business days from the time you submit your trip. The timeline depends on trip complexity."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What if my trip details change after submission?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "You can update your trip details after submission and before the review is finalized. If a change is significant, your analyst will re-evaluate the affected sections."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Can I communicate directly with my analyst?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Your analyst's findings and recommendations are delivered through the SafeTrekr platform as part of your Trip Safety Binder."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Is the review the same for a domestic day trip and an international mission trip?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Every trip receives the same 17-section framework, but the depth and focus of each section adapts to your trip type."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "What happens if the analyst finds a serious risk?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "If your analyst identifies a significant risk, it is documented in Section 12 (Known Issues and Flags) with a severity rating and a specific recommendation."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "How is this different from a travel advisory?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Government travel advisories are country-level assessments updated periodically. A SafeTrekr analyst review is trip-specific, destination-specific, date-specific, and group-specific."
            }
          },
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": "Can I share the review with my board or insurance carrier?",
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": "Yes. Your Trip Safety Binder is designed to be shared with boards, insurance carriers, legal counsel, and any stakeholder who needs to see your safety documentation."
            }
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "@type": "Service",
        "name": "Analyst Safety Review",
        "provider": {
          "@type": "Organization",
          "name": "SafeTrekr"
        },
        "description": "Every trip professionally reviewed across 17 safety sections by a trained analyst.",
        "serviceType": "Safety Review"
      }
    ]
  }
  </script>

  <style>
    /* ---- Glassmorphic header ---- */
    .header-scrolled {
      background: rgba(231, 236, 238, 0.80);
      backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(184, 195, 199, 0.5);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }

    /* ---- Mobile menu overlay ---- */
    .mobile-menu-overlay {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(6, 26, 35, 0.5);
      z-index: 40;
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }
    .mobile-menu-overlay.active {
      opacity: 1;
      pointer-events: all;
    }
    .mobile-menu-panel {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: min(320px, 85vw);
      background: var(--color-card);
      z-index: 50;
      transform: translateX(100%);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      overflow-y: auto;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .mobile-menu-panel.active {
      transform: translateX(0);
    }

    /* ---- Progress bar fill ---- */
    @keyframes progressFill {
      from { width: 0; }
      to { width: 70%; }
    }
    .progress-fill-hero {
      animation: progressFill 1s ease-out forwards;
      animation-delay: 0.8s;
      width: 0;
    }

    /* ---- Fade-up animation ---- */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .animate-fade-up {
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease-out forwards;
      opacity: 0;
    }

    /* ---- Scale-in for hero card ---- */
    @keyframes scaleIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.95); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    }
    .animate-scale-in {
      animation: scaleIn 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4,0,0.2,1) forwards;
      opacity: 0;
    }

    /* ---- Accordion ---- */
    .accordion-content {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
    }
    .accordion-content.open {
      max-height: 2000px;
    }
    .accordion-chevron {
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    .accordion-chevron.rotated {
      transform: rotate(180deg);
    }
    .accordion-trigger:hover {
      background: rgba(241,249,244,0.5);
    }
    .accordion-trigger.active-trigger {
      background: rgba(241,249,244,0.3);
    }

    /* ---- FAQ accordion ---- */
    .faq-content {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
    }
    .faq-content.open {
      max-height: 800px;
    }

    /* ---- Timeline connecting line ---- */
    .timeline-line {
      stroke-dasharray: 6 4;
    }

    /* ---- Scrollspy active ---- */
    .scrollspy-link {
      transition: color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .scrollspy-link.active {
      color: var(--color-primary-700);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* ---- Comparison table SafeTrekr column ---- */
    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
      .comparison-table td:nth-child(2),
      .comparison-table th:nth-child(2) {
        background: rgba(241,249,244,0.4);
      }
    }

    /* ---- Stacked paper effect ---- */
    .doc-preview-stack {
      position: relative;
    }
    .doc-preview-stack::before,
    .doc-preview-stack::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 8px;
      left: 50%;
      width: 90%;
      height: 100%;
      background: var(--color-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: -1;
    }
    .doc-preview-stack::after {
      top: 16px;
      width: 82%;
      opacity: 0.6;
      z-index: -2;
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .progress-fill-hero { animation: none; width: 70%; }
      .animate-fade-up { animation: none; opacity: 1; transform: none; }
      .animate-scale-in { animation: none; opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ================================================================
       SKIP NAV
       ================================================================ -->
  <a href="#main-content" class="sr-only focus:not-sr-only focus:absolute focus:top-4 focus:left-4 focus:z-50 focus:px-4 focus:py-2 focus:bg-primary-700 focus:text-white focus:rounded-md">Skip to main content</a>

  <!-- ================================================================
       HEADER
       ================================================================ -->
  <header id="site-header" class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-30 transition-all duration-300" style="height: 80px;">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12 h-full flex items-center justify-between">
      <!-- Logo: Horizontal lockup -->
      <a href="/" aria-label="SafeTrekr home" class="flex-shrink-0">
        <svg height="32" viewBox="0 0 180 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="hidden lg:block" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M16 1L3 8v10c0 7.2 5.5 13.9 13 15.9 7.5-2 13-8.7 13-15.9V8L16 1z" fill="none" stroke="#123646" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M10 14l4 4 8-8" stroke="#3f885b" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <text x="40" y="22" font-family="Plus Jakarta Sans, system-ui, sans-serif" font-weight="700" font-size="18" fill="#123646">SafeTrekr</text>
        </svg>
        <svg height="28" viewBox="0 0 180 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="lg:hidden" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M16 1L3 8v10c0 7.2 5.5 13.9 13 15.9 7.5-2 13-8.7 13-15.9V8L16 1z" fill="none" stroke="#123646" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M10 14l4 4 8-8" stroke="#3f885b" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <text x="40" y="22" font-family="Plus Jakarta Sans, system-ui, sans-serif" font-weight="700" font-size="18" fill="#123646">SafeTrekr</text>
        </svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Desktop Nav -->
      <nav aria-label="Main navigation" class="hidden lg:flex items-center gap-8">
        <a href="/platform" class="text-base font-medium text-foreground/70 hover:text-foreground transition-colors duration-150 flex items-center gap-1" style="font-family: var(--font-body);">
          Platform
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 opacity-50" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/solutions" class="text-base font-medium text-foreground/70 hover:text-foreground transition-colors duration-150 flex items-center gap-1" style="font-family: var(--font-body);">
          Solutions
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 opacity-50" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/how-it-works" class="text-base font-medium text-foreground/70 hover:text-foreground transition-colors duration-150" style="font-family: var(--font-body);">How It Works</a>
        <a href="/pricing" class="text-base font-medium text-foreground/70 hover:text-foreground transition-colors duration-150" style="font-family: var(--font-body);">Pricing</a>
        <a href="/resources" class="text-base font-medium text-foreground/70 hover:text-foreground transition-colors duration-150 flex items-center gap-1" style="font-family: var(--font-body);">
          Resources
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 opacity-50" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </nav>

      <!-- Desktop CTAs -->
      <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://app.safetrekr.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm font-semibold transition-colors duration-150 hover:text-foreground" style="font-family: var(--font-heading); color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Sign In</a>
        <a href="/demo" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center font-semibold rounded-md transition-all duration-150 text-white" style="font-family: var(--font-heading); background: var(--color-primary-600); padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 15px; border-radius: var(--radius-md); text-decoration: none;">Get a Demo</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Mobile Hamburger -->
      <button id="mobile-menu-btn" class="lg:hidden p-2 text-foreground" aria-label="Open navigation menu" aria-expanded="false">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"/>
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Mobile Menu -->
  <div id="mobile-overlay" class="mobile-menu-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div id="mobile-panel" class="mobile-menu-panel" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-label="Main navigation">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-8">
      <span class="font-display font-bold text-lg text-foreground">Menu</span>
      <button id="mobile-close-btn" class="p-2 text-foreground" aria-label="Close navigation menu">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
      </button>
    </div>
    <nav class="flex flex-col gap-2">
      <a href="/platform" class="py-3 px-4 rounded-md text-base font-medium text-foreground hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors" style="font-family: var(--font-body);">Platform</a>
      <a href="/solutions" class="py-3 px-4 rounded-md text-base font-medium text-foreground hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors" style="font-family: var(--font-body);">Solutions</a>
      <a href="/how-it-works" class="py-3 px-4 rounded-md text-base font-medium text-foreground hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors" style="font-family: var(--font-body);">How It Works</a>
      <a href="/pricing" class="py-3 px-4 rounded-md text-base font-medium text-foreground hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors" style="font-family: var(--font-body);">Pricing</a>
      <a href="/resources" class="py-3 px-4 rounded-md text-base font-medium text-foreground hover:bg-primary-50 transition-colors" style="font-family: var(--font-body);">Resources</a>
      <div class="border-t mt-4 pt-4" style="border-color: var(--color-border);">
        <a href="/demo" class="block w-full text-center py-3 rounded-md text-base font-semibold text-white" style="background: var(--color-primary-600); font-family: var(--font-heading);">Get a Demo</a>
      </div>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <!-- ================================================================
       MAIN CONTENT
       ================================================================ -->
  <main id="main-content">

    <!-- ================================================================
         SECTION 1: HERO
         ================================================================ -->
    <section aria-labelledby="hero-heading" class="pt-24 pb-16 lg:pt-28 lg:pb-24" style="background: var(--color-background);">
      <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">

        <!-- Breadcrumb -->
        <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="mb-8">
          <ol class="hidden sm:flex items-center gap-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); font-family: var(--font-body);">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors">Home</a></li>
            <li><span class="mx-1">/</span></li>
            <li><a href="/platform" class="hover:text-foreground transition-colors">Platform</a></li>
            <li><span class="mx-1">/</span></li>
            <li><span aria-current="page" style="color: var(--color-foreground); font-weight: 500;">Analyst Safety Review</span></li>
          </ol>
          <a href="/platform" class="sm:hidden inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm hover:text-foreground transition-colors" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); font-family: var(--font-body);">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to Platform
          </a>
        </nav>

        <!-- 2-Column Hero -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">

          <!-- Left: Text -->
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 80ms;">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" style="color: var(--color-primary-700);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
              <span class="text-eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-primary-700);">ANALYST REVIEW</span>
            </div>

            <h1 id="hero-heading" class="text-display-lg mb-6 animate-fade-up" style="color: var(--color-foreground); max-width: 20ch; animation-delay: 160ms;">
              Every Trip Reviewed by a Safety Analyst.
            </h1>

            <p class="text-body-lg mb-10 animate-fade-up" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); max-width: 65ch; animation-delay: 240ms;">
              No algorithm. No checklist. A trained professional reviews your trip across 17 structured safety sections -- from destination intelligence to emergency preparedness to compliance documentation.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay: 320ms;">
              <a href="/resources/sample-binders" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" style="padding: 16px 32px; font-size: 16px;">
                See a Sample Review
              </a>
              <a href="/demo" class="btn btn-lg btn-secondary" style="padding: 16px 32px; font-size: 16px;">
                Request a Demo
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Right: Hero Composition Panel -->
          <div class="animate-scale-in" style="animation-delay: 400ms;">
            <div class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl border p-6 lg:p-8 max-w-[480px] lg:ml-auto" style="background: var(--color-card); border-color: var(--color-border);">

              <span class="text-eyebrow block mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary-700);">ANALYST REVIEW</span>
              <span class="badge badge-brand mb-4 inline-block">In Progress</span>

              <h3 class="text-heading-sm mb-1" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Spring Field Trip</h3>
              <p class="text-body-sm mb-6" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Springfield USD</p>

              <!-- Progress Bar -->
              <div class="mb-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background: var(--color-primary-100);" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="12" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="17" aria-label="Review progress: 12 of 17 sections reviewed">
                <div class="h-2 rounded-full progress-fill-hero" style="background: var(--color-primary-500);"></div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs mb-6" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">12 of 17 sections reviewed</p>

              <!-- Checklist Preview -->
              <div role="list" class="space-y-2">
                <div role="listitem" class="flex items-center gap-3" aria-label="Completed: Destination Safety">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                  <span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Destination Safety</span>
                </div>
                <div role="listitem" class="flex items-center gap-3" aria-label="Completed: Transportation">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                  <span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Transportation</span>
                </div>
                <div role="listitem" class="flex items-center gap-3" aria-label="Completed: Emergency Prep">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                  <span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Emergency Prep</span>
                </div>
                <div role="listitem" class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full border-2 flex-shrink-0" style="border-color: var(--color-border);"></div>
                  <span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Compliance Docs</span>
                </div>
                <div role="listitem" class="flex items-center gap-3">
                  <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full border-2 flex-shrink-0" style="border-color: var(--color-border);"></div>
                  <span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Final Approval</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ================================================================
         SECTION 2: WHO ARE THE ANALYSTS (DARK)
         ================================================================ -->
    <section id="analysts" aria-labelledby="analysts-heading" data-theme="dark" style="background: var(--color-secondary); padding: 96px 0;">
      <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">

        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-eyebrow block mb-4" style="color: var(--color-primary-400);">YOUR SAFETY TEAM</span>
          <h2 id="analysts-heading" class="text-display-md mb-6" style="color: #f7f8f8; max-width: 28ch; margin: 0 auto;">
            Trained Analysts. Not Algorithms.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body-lg mx-auto" style="color: var(--color-secondary-muted); max-width: 65ch;">
            Every SafeTrekr review is conducted by a trained safety analyst -- not generated by software, not assembled from templates, not outsourced to a call center. Your analyst reads every detail of your trip plan and evaluates it against real-world conditions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Credential Cards -->
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">

          <!-- Card 1: Professionally Trained -->
          <article class="rounded-xl p-6 lg:p-8" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
            <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6" style="background: rgba(76,164,110,0.1);">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: var(--color-primary-400);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-heading-sm mb-3" style="color: #f7f8f8; font-weight: 600;">Professionally Trained</h3>
            <p class="text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-secondary-muted);">Every analyst completes a structured training program covering risk assessment methodology, government intelligence interpretation, and SafeTrekr's 17-section review framework before conducting a single review.</p>
          </article>

          <!-- Card 2: Standardized Methodology -->
          <article class="rounded-xl p-6 lg:p-8" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
            <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6" style="background: rgba(76,164,110,0.1);">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: var(--color-primary-400);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 014 4v14a3 3 0 00-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 00-4 4v14a3 3 0 013-3h7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-heading-sm mb-3" style="color: #f7f8f8; font-weight: 600;">Standardized Methodology</h3>
            <p class="text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-secondary-muted);">Analysts follow a documented, repeatable methodology for every review. The same 17 sections. The same evaluation criteria. The same evidence standards. Consistency you can audit.</p>
          </article>

          <!-- Card 3: Dedicated Assignment -->
          <article class="rounded-xl p-6 lg:p-8 sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
            <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6" style="background: rgba(76,164,110,0.1);">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: var(--color-primary-400);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H6a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><polyline points="16 11 18 13 22 9"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-heading-sm mb-3" style="color: #f7f8f8; font-weight: 600;">Dedicated Assignment</h3>
            <p class="text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-secondary-muted);">Your trip is assigned to a specific analyst who owns the review from start to finish. One person. Full accountability. Direct findings and recommendations -- not a committee output.</p>
          </article>
        </div>

        <!-- Process Strip -->
        <div class="rounded-xl p-6 lg:p-8" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6" role="list">

            <div role="listitem" class="text-center">
              <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full mx-auto flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background: rgba(76,164,110,0.2); color: var(--color-primary-400); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; font-family: var(--font-heading);">1</div>
              <h4 class="text-heading-sm mb-2" style="color: #f7f8f8; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">Trip Assigned</h4>
              <p class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-secondary-muted);">Your submission is routed to an available analyst with relevant expertise for your destination and trip type.</p>
            </div>

            <div role="listitem" class="text-center">
              <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full mx-auto flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background: rgba(76,164,110,0.2); color: var(--color-primary-400); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; font-family: var(--font-heading);">2</div>
              <h4 class="text-heading-sm mb-2" style="color: #f7f8f8; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">Full-Context Read</h4>
              <p class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-secondary-muted);">The analyst reads your complete trip plan -- destination, dates, participants, activities, logistics, and any concerns you flagged.</p>
            </div>

            <div role="listitem" class="text-center">
              <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full mx-auto flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background: rgba(76,164,110,0.2); color: var(--color-primary-400); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; font-family: var(--font-heading);">3</div>
              <h4 class="text-heading-sm mb-2" style="color: #f7f8f8; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">17-Section Evaluation</h4>
              <p class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-secondary-muted);">Each section is evaluated against current conditions, government intelligence data, and SafeTrekr's evidence standards.</p>
            </div>

            <div role="listitem" class="text-center">
              <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full mx-auto flex items-center justify-center mb-4" style="background: rgba(76,164,110,0.2); color: var(--color-primary-400); font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; font-family: var(--font-heading);">4</div>
              <h4 class="text-heading-sm mb-2" style="color: #f7f8f8; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">Findings Delivered</h4>
              <p class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-secondary-muted);">The analyst writes specific findings and actionable recommendations. No boilerplate. Every finding references your trip.</p>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cross-Link -->
        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <a href="/about/analysts" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-body-md transition-colors hover:underline" style="color: var(--color-primary-400); font-weight: 500;">
            Meet our full analyst team
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ================================================================
         SECTION 3: INTERACTIVE 17-SECTION REVIEW GRID
         ================================================================ -->
    <section id="review-sections" aria-labelledby="review-sections-heading" style="background: var(--color-background); padding: 96px 0;">
      <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">

        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" style="color: var(--color-primary-700);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            <span class="text-eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-primary-700);">THE 17 SECTIONS</span>
          </div>
          <h2 id="review-sections-heading" class="text-display-md mb-4" style="color: var(--color-foreground); max-width: 28ch; margin: 0 auto;">
            Every Detail Evaluated.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-body-lg mx-auto" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); max-width: 65ch;">
            Your analyst reviews your trip across 17 structured sections organized into 5 categories. Expand any section to see exactly what is evaluated and why.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Category Accordion Groups -->
        <div class="space-y-8" id="review-grid">

          <!-- ============ CATEGORY 1: TRIP PLANNING ============ -->
          <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden" style="background: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);">
            <!-- Category Header -->
            <div class="px-6 lg:px-8 py-5 flex items-center justify-between" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <span class="badge badge-brand" style="font-size: 11px;">4 SECTIONS</span>
                <h3 class="text-heading-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground); font-weight: 600;">Trip Planning</h3>
              </div>
              <span class="text-body-sm hidden lg:block" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Sections 1-4</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Sections -->
            <div style="border-top: 0;">

              <!-- Section 1: Overview -->
              <div class="border-b" style="border-color: var(--color-border);">
                <button class="accordion-trigger w-full px-6 lg:px-8 py-4 flex items-center gap-4 cursor-pointer transition-colors" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="section-1-content" id="section-1-trigger" onclick="toggleSection(1)">
                  <span class="h-7 w-7 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-semibold" style="background: var(--color-primary-50); color: var(--color-primary-700); font-family: var(--font-heading);">1</span>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
                  <span class="flex-1 text-left text-body-lg font-medium" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Overview</span>
                  <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" id="chevron-1"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-content" id="section-1-content" role="region" aria-labelledby="section-1-trigger">
                  <div class="px-6 lg:px-8 pb-6" style="padding-left: calc(1.5rem + 1.75rem + 1rem + 1.25rem + 1rem);">
                    <p class="text-body-md mb-4" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Trip purpose, objectives, organizational context, and overall scope of the travel plan.</p>
                    <div class="space-y-2 mb-4">
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Stated trip objectives and educational or organizational goals</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Group composition and organizational affiliation</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Trip duration and seasonal timing considerations</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Historical context if this is a recurring trip</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 p-4 rounded-lg" style="background: rgba(241,249,244,0.5); border-left: 2px solid var(--color-primary-300);">
                      <span class="text-eyebrow block mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary-700); font-size: 11px;">WHY THIS MATTERS</span>
                      <p class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">A clear trip overview ensures the analyst understands the full context of your travel. Ambiguous objectives can mask risks that become apparent only when the purpose is well-defined.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Section 2: Participants -->
              <div class="border-b" style="border-color: var(--color-border);">
                <button class="accordion-trigger w-full px-6 lg:px-8 py-4 flex items-center gap-4 cursor-pointer transition-colors" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="section-2-content" id="section-2-trigger" onclick="toggleSection(2)">
                  <span class="h-7 w-7 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-semibold" style="background: var(--color-primary-50); color: var(--color-primary-700); font-family: var(--font-heading);">2</span>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
                  <span class="flex-1 text-left text-body-lg font-medium" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Participants</span>
                  <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" id="chevron-2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-content" id="section-2-content" role="region" aria-labelledby="section-2-trigger">
                  <div class="px-6 lg:px-8 pb-6" style="padding-left: calc(1.5rem + 1.75rem + 1rem + 1.25rem + 1rem);">
                    <p class="text-body-md mb-4" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Participant count, demographics, age ranges, special needs, medical considerations, and chaperone-to-participant ratios.</p>
                    <div class="space-y-2 mb-4">
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Total participant count and age distribution</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Chaperone-to-participant ratio against best-practice standards</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Medical conditions, allergies, or mobility requirements</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Experience level of participants for planned activities</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Special accommodations or dietary needs</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 p-4 rounded-lg" style="background: rgba(241,249,244,0.5); border-left: 2px solid var(--color-primary-300);">
                      <span class="text-eyebrow block mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary-700); font-size: 11px;">WHY THIS MATTERS</span>
                      <p class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">The participant profile directly determines risk thresholds. A group of 12-year-olds hiking requires fundamentally different safety planning than a corporate leadership retreat. Your analyst calibrates every finding to your specific group.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Section 3: Itinerary -->
              <div class="border-b" style="border-color: var(--color-border);">
                <button class="accordion-trigger w-full px-6 lg:px-8 py-4 flex items-center gap-4 cursor-pointer transition-colors" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="section-3-content" id="section-3-trigger" onclick="toggleSection(3)">
                  <span class="h-7 w-7 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-semibold" style="background: var(--color-primary-50); color: var(--color-primary-700); font-family: var(--font-heading);">3</span>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
                  <span class="flex-1 text-left text-body-lg font-medium" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Itinerary</span>
                  <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" id="chevron-3"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-content" id="section-3-content" role="region" aria-labelledby="section-3-trigger">
                  <div class="px-6 lg:px-8 pb-6" style="padding-left: calc(1.5rem + 1.75rem + 1rem + 1.25rem + 1rem);">
                    <p class="text-body-md mb-4" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Day-by-day schedule, activity timing, transit windows, rest periods, and contingency buffers.</p>
                    <div class="space-y-2 mb-4">
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Complete day-by-day activity schedule</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Transit times between locations with realistic buffers</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Rest periods and meal breaks</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Free time windows and supervision plans</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Schedule contingency for weather or disruption</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 p-4 rounded-lg" style="background: rgba(241,249,244,0.5); border-left: 2px solid var(--color-primary-300);">
                      <span class="text-eyebrow block mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary-700); font-size: 11px;">WHY THIS MATTERS</span>
                      <p class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Overpacked itineraries create fatigue-related risks. Tight transit windows leave no margin for delays. Your analyst evaluates whether the schedule is realistic and safe for your specific group.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Section 4: Transportation -->
              <div>
                <button class="accordion-trigger w-full px-6 lg:px-8 py-4 flex items-center gap-4 cursor-pointer transition-colors" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="section-4-content" id="section-4-trigger" onclick="toggleSection(4)">
                  <span class="h-7 w-7 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-semibold" style="background: var(--color-primary-50); color: var(--color-primary-700); font-family: var(--font-heading);">4</span>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M8 6v6"/><path d="M15 6v6"/><path d="M2 12h19.6"/><path d="M18 18h3s.5-1.7.8-2.8c.1-.4.2-.8.2-1.2 0-.4-.1-.8-.2-1.2l-1.4-5C20.1 6.8 19.1 6 18 6H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v10h3"/><circle cx="7" cy="18" r="2"/><path d="M9 18h5"/><circle cx="16" cy="18" r="2"/></svg>
                  <span class="flex-1 text-left text-body-lg font-medium" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Transportation</span>
                  <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" id="chevron-4"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="accordion-content" id="section-4-content" role="region" aria-labelledby="section-4-trigger">
                  <div class="px-6 lg:px-8 pb-6" style="padding-left: calc(1.5rem + 1.75rem + 1rem + 1.25rem + 1rem);">
                    <p class="text-body-md mb-4" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Ground transportation providers, vehicle safety records, driver credentials, and route risk assessment.</p>
                    <div class="space-y-2 mb-4">
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Ground transportation provider verification</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Vehicle type, capacity, and safety equipment</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Driver credential verification requirements</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Route assessment including road conditions and construction</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Backup transportation contingency</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 p-4 rounded-lg" style="background: rgba(241,249,244,0.5); border-left: 2px solid var(--color-primary-300);">
                      <span class="text-eyebrow block mb-2" style="color: var(--color-primary-700); font-size: 11px;">WHY THIS MATTERS</span>
                      <p class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Transportation incidents are among the most common and preventable risks in group travel. Verifying provider safety records and assessing route conditions are foundational to any responsible trip plan.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- ============ CATEGORY 2: DESTINATIONS & VENUES ============ -->
