                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Airline safety record and operational reliability</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Airport security and accessibility at origin and destination</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Layover duration, airport facilities, and connection risks</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Arrival timing relative to local conditions and transportation availability</span></div>
                      <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Group seating and baggage logistics for participant count</span></div>
