                      <p class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Missed connections, overnight layovers in unfamiliar airports, and arrival into destinations after dark create cascading risks. Your analyst evaluates the full air travel chain -- not just the ticket.</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Section 6: Lodging -->
              <div class="border-b" style="border-color: var(--color-border);">
                <button class="accordion-trigger w-full px-6 lg:px-8 py-4 flex items-center gap-4 cursor-pointer transition-colors" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="section-6-content" id="section-6-trigger" onclick="toggleSection(6)">
                  <span class="h-7 w-7 rounded-full flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-semibold" style="background: var(--color-primary-50); color: var(--color-primary-700); font-family: var(--font-heading);">6</span>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M6 22V4a2 2 0 012-2h8a2 2 0 012 2v18z"/><path d="M6 12H4a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2"/><path d="M18 9h2a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2"/><path d="M10 6h4"/><path d="M10 10h4"/><path d="M10 14h4"/><path d="M10 18h4"/></svg>
                  <span class="flex-1 text-left text-body-lg font-medium" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Lodging</span>
                  <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" id="chevron-6"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
