                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Trained analyst evaluates every section</span></div></td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); opacity: 0.5;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Self-assessed by trip organizer</span></div></td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);" class="hover:bg-primary-50/30 transition-colors">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Government intelligence data</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">5 sources: NOAA, USGS, CDC, GDACS, ReliefWeb</span> <span class="badge badge-brand ml-2" style="font-size: 10px;">ADVANCED</span></div></td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); opacity: 0.5;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Not available</span></div></td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);" class="hover:bg-primary-50/30 transition-colors">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Monte Carlo risk scoring</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Probability-weighted scores per destination</span> <span class="badge badge-brand ml-2" style="font-size: 10px;">ADVANCED</span></div></td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); opacity: 0.5;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">No quantitative scoring</span></div></td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);" class="hover:bg-primary-50/30 transition-colors">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">17-section structured review</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Standardized methodology, every trip</span></div></td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-safety-yellow);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Ad hoc checklist, inconsistent scope</span></div></td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);" class="hover:bg-primary-50/30 transition-colors">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Specific findings &amp; recommendations</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Written for your trip, your group, your destination</span></div></td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); opacity: 0.5;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Generic guidance at best</span></div></td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);" class="hover:bg-primary-50/30 transition-colors">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Emergency preparedness evaluation</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Rally points, evacuation routes, hospital mapping</span></div></td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-safety-yellow);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Basic emergency contact list</span></div></td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);" class="hover:bg-primary-50/30 transition-colors">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Tamper-evident documentation</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">SHA-256 hash chain, audit-ready</span> <span class="badge badge-brand ml-2" style="font-size: 10px;">ADVANCED</span></div></td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); opacity: 0.5;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Editable documents, no integrity proof</span></div></td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);" class="hover:bg-primary-50/30 transition-colors">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Compliance documentation</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Built for board, insurance, and regulatory review</span></div></td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-safety-yellow);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="8" y1="12" x2="16" y2="12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Informal records, no standard format</span></div></td>
              </tr>
              <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);" class="hover:bg-primary-50/30 transition-colors">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Turnaround time</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">3-5 business days, no staff time</span></div></td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); opacity: 0.5;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">$700-$1,400 in staff time per trip</span></div></td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="hover:bg-primary-50/30 transition-colors">
                <td class="px-6 py-4 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Ongoing intelligence updates</td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-primary-500);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Data refreshed until departure date</span></div></td>
                <td class="px-6 py-4"><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); opacity: 0.5;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/></svg><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">Static at time of creation</span></div></td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <!-- Mobile Comparison Cards -->
        <div class="lg:hidden space-y-3" id="mobile-comparison">
          <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);"><p class="text-body-md font-medium mb-3" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Professional risk assessment</p><div class="flex items-start gap-2 mb-2"><span class="badge badge-brand" style="font-size: 10px;">SAFETREKR</span><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Trained analyst evaluates every section</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">DIY: Self-assessed by trip organizer</span></div></div>
          <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);"><p class="text-body-md font-medium mb-3" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Government intelligence data</p><div class="flex items-start gap-2 mb-2"><span class="badge badge-brand" style="font-size: 10px;">SAFETREKR</span><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">5 sources: NOAA, USGS, CDC, GDACS, ReliefWeb</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">DIY: Not available</span></div></div>
          <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);"><p class="text-body-md font-medium mb-3" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Monte Carlo risk scoring</p><div class="flex items-start gap-2 mb-2"><span class="badge badge-brand" style="font-size: 10px;">SAFETREKR</span><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Probability-weighted scores per destination</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">DIY: No quantitative scoring</span></div></div>
          <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);"><p class="text-body-md font-medium mb-3" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">17-section structured review</p><div class="flex items-start gap-2 mb-2"><span class="badge badge-brand" style="font-size: 10px;">SAFETREKR</span><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Standardized methodology, every trip</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">DIY: Ad hoc checklist, inconsistent scope</span></div></div>
          <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);"><p class="text-body-md font-medium mb-3" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Specific findings &amp; recommendations</p><div class="flex items-start gap-2 mb-2"><span class="badge badge-brand" style="font-size: 10px;">SAFETREKR</span><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Written for your trip, your group, your destination</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">DIY: Generic guidance at best</span></div></div>
          <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);"><p class="text-body-md font-medium mb-3" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Tamper-evident documentation</p><div class="flex items-start gap-2 mb-2"><span class="badge badge-brand" style="font-size: 10px;">SAFETREKR</span><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">SHA-256 hash chain, audit-ready</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">DIY: Editable documents, no integrity proof</span></div></div>
          <div class="rounded-lg p-4" style="background: var(--color-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-border);"><p class="text-body-md font-medium mb-3" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">Turnaround time</p><div class="flex items-start gap-2 mb-2"><span class="badge badge-brand" style="font-size: 10px;">SAFETREKR</span><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-foreground);">3-5 business days, no staff time</span></div><div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-body-sm" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);">DIY: $700-$1,400 in staff time per trip</span></div></div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ================================================================
         SECTION 8: FAQ
         ================================================================ -->
    <section id="faq" aria-labelledby="faq-heading" style="background: var(--color-card); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); padding: 96px 0;">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">

        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <span class="text-eyebrow block mb-4" style="color: var(--color-primary-700);">COMMON QUESTIONS</span>
          <h2 id="faq-heading" class="text-display-md" style="color: var(--color-foreground); max-width: 28ch; margin: 0 auto;">
            Analyst Review FAQ
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div id="faq-accordion" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">

          <!-- FAQ 1 -->
          <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <button class="w-full py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
              <span class="text-heading-sm pr-4" style="color: var(--color-foreground); font-weight: 600;">Who are the safety analysts?</span>
              <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-content">
              <p class="pb-5 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); max-width: 65ch;">Every SafeTrekr analyst is a trained professional who has completed our structured training program covering risk assessment methodology, government intelligence interpretation, and the 17-section review framework. They are not volunteers, not contractors pulled from a gig platform, and not customer support agents following a script. Each analyst maintains ongoing certification in SafeTrekr's review methodology.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 2 -->
          <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <button class="w-full py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
              <span class="text-heading-sm pr-4" style="color: var(--color-foreground); font-weight: 600;">How long does a review take?</span>
              <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-content">
              <p class="pb-5 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); max-width: 65ch;">Most reviews are completed in 3-5 business days from the time you submit your trip. The timeline depends on trip complexity -- a domestic day trip is typically faster than a multi-country international itinerary. Your analyst works through all 17 sections with the same thoroughness regardless of trip type.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 3 -->
          <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <button class="w-full py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
              <span class="text-heading-sm pr-4" style="color: var(--color-foreground); font-weight: 600;">What if my trip details change after submission?</span>
              <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-content">
              <p class="pb-5 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); max-width: 65ch;">You can update your trip details after submission and before the review is finalized. If a change is significant -- such as a new destination or major itinerary revision -- your analyst will re-evaluate the affected sections. Minor changes (participant count adjustments, schedule tweaks) are incorporated without extending the timeline.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 4 -->
          <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <button class="w-full py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
              <span class="text-heading-sm pr-4" style="color: var(--color-foreground); font-weight: 600;">Can I communicate directly with my analyst?</span>
              <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-content">
              <p class="pb-5 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); max-width: 65ch;">Your analyst's findings and recommendations are delivered through the SafeTrekr platform as part of your Trip Safety Binder. The review process is structured to ensure consistency and thoroughness. If you have specific concerns about your trip, include them in the submission form and your analyst will address them in the relevant sections.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 5 -->
          <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <button class="w-full py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
              <span class="text-heading-sm pr-4" style="color: var(--color-foreground); font-weight: 600;">Is the review the same for a domestic day trip and an international mission trip?</span>
              <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-content">
              <p class="pb-5 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); max-width: 65ch;">Every trip receives the same 17-section framework, but the depth and focus of each section adapts to your trip type. A domestic field trip may have minimal air travel or lodging concerns but significant venue and transportation evaluation. An international mission trip will have extensive destination safety, health advisory, and emergency preparedness analysis. The framework is consistent; the content is specific to your trip.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 6 -->
          <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <button class="w-full py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
              <span class="text-heading-sm pr-4" style="color: var(--color-foreground); font-weight: 600;">What happens if the analyst finds a serious risk?</span>
              <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-content">
              <p class="pb-5 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); max-width: 65ch;">If your analyst identifies a significant risk, it is documented in Section 12 (Known Issues and Flags) with a severity rating and a specific recommendation. High-severity findings are highlighted in the binder summary. SafeTrekr does not make go/no-go decisions for your organization -- we provide the evidence and recommendations so your leadership can make informed decisions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 7 -->
          <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <button class="w-full py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
              <span class="text-heading-sm pr-4" style="color: var(--color-foreground); font-weight: 600;">How is this different from a travel advisory?</span>
              <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-content">
              <p class="pb-5 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); max-width: 65ch;">Government travel advisories are country-level assessments updated periodically. A SafeTrekr analyst review is trip-specific, destination-specific, date-specific, and group-specific. We evaluate your exact itinerary against current conditions using 5 government data sources, then write findings that reference your group size, your venues, your transportation, and your timeline. A travel advisory tells you a country has risk. An analyst review tells you what that risk means for your specific trip.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- FAQ 8 -->
          <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
            <button class="w-full py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleFaq(this)" aria-expanded="false">
              <span class="text-heading-sm pr-4" style="color: var(--color-foreground); font-weight: 600;">Can I share the review with my board or insurance carrier?</span>
              <svg class="accordion-chevron w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground);" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-content">
              <p class="pb-5 text-body-md" style="color: var(--color-muted-foreground); max-width: 65ch;">Yes. Your Trip Safety Binder is designed to be shared with boards, insurance carriers, legal counsel, and any stakeholder who needs to see your safety documentation. The SHA-256 tamper-evident integrity means any recipient can verify the document has not been modified since it was created. Many organizations use the binder specifically for board presentations and insurance documentation.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


